# Change management over the automated control.
#
# Pull requests that touch the control logic, its configuration, or the
# monitoring/escalation automation require review by the control owner before
# merge. Enforce this by enabling branch protection on `main` with
# "Require a pull request before merging" and "Require review from Code Owners".
#
# In an organization, replace @MaxwellM-GRC with a governance team,
# e.g. @your-org/grc-controls, so review does not depend on one individual.

# Default owner for everything in the repo.
*                        @MaxwellM-GRC

# Control logic and parameters (most sensitive: detection rules and SLAs).
/src/detection.py        @MaxwellM-GRC
/src/correlation.py      @MaxwellM-GRC
/config.yaml             @MaxwellM-GRC

# Monitoring, alerting, and escalation automation.
/.github/workflows/      @MaxwellM-GRC
